resources.name: Create user(donor) with sucess 201
resources.description:
### Send body fields required: 
- email - must be type string  
- password - must be type string  
- name - must be type string  
- isAdm - must be type boolean  
- cnpj/cpf - must be type string  
- responsible - must be type string  
- contact - must be type string  
- address - must be type string  
- number - must be type string  
- complement - must be type string  
- city - must be type string  
- state - must be type string  
- zipCode - must be type string  

---  

### Authentication not required  

---  
 
```response:201
{
"email": "kenzinho@mail.com",
"name": "kenzinho",
"cnpj/cpf": "11111111111",
"id": "8e350ad5-467f-41b6-9abf-a320c94885ca",
"address": {
	"id": "464c3018-11c9-468d-8696-08fcb93b8504",
	"address": "rua qualquer",
	"complement": "apto 99",
	"city": "Porto Alegre",
	"state": "RS",
	"zipCode": "11222000"
	},
"responsible": "José",
"contact": "Maria",
"type": "donor",
"isAdm": "false"
}
```
